title: What is a combinatorial interpretation?
abstract:
Abstract.
In this survey we discuss the notion of combinatorial
interpretation in the context of Algebraic Combinatorics and related
areas. We approach the subject from the Computational Complexity
perspective. We review many examples, state a workable definition,
discuss many open problems, and present recent results on the subject.
